Utterance.UttText: Bed 2 in room 1, Paulos Gomez Castillo, 74 yrs old under Dr Willough, came in with kidney stones.
With a very long cardiac history just see the notes.

Phrase.PhraseText: With a very long cardiac history just

Utterance.UttText: He just came in not too long ago.
He's got multiple allergies. on soft cut up diet.
Obs are all stable, He's got VRE on contact precautions, he is awaiting chest xray.
He is NFR but still for mets.
He is a bit confused at times and can be very agitated.
He is of a non English background.
He is 2 staff assist when walking using FASF (forearm support frame) He's got IDC insitu on FBC.(fluid balance chart).
